Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.18,0:00:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.75,0:00:10.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我試著像奈亞拉托提普一樣在夜裡潛行過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.01,0:00:12.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一點也不好笑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.70,0:00:14.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒人能打擾我們
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.19,0:00:17.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我已經為此先下手了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.41,0:00:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧  整個夜晚都是屬於我倆的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.52,0:00:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你知道你在做什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.20,0:00:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧  真尋
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.42,0:00:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  奈亞子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.97,0:00:35.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們製造愛的結晶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.18,0:00:38.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不要
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.45,0:00:57.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好八坂  起床了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.76,0:00:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要一起去吃早飯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.64,0:01:01.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  好啊好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.57,0:01:02.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.93,0:01:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間正好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.46,0:01:06.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  我的眼睛  眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.52,0:01:11.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是一時鬼迷心竅  只是衝動啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.07,0:01:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  我們就來一次  求你了求你了  就一次
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.20,0:01:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真尋！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.51,0:01:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}早上好  余市
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.99,0:01:08.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}睡得好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.28,0:01:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}嗯  很安穩  你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.92,0:01:15.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}我好像做了個噩夢
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------TXTA-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.92,0:02:52.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太過分了吧  真尋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.38,0:02:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底誰過分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.66,0:02:56.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是你意圖打擾我安穩的睡眠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.29,0:02:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才沒有做這種事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.49,0:03:01.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒不如說那是我對你的愛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.20,0:03:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只是在給我添麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.20,0:03:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼什麼  在說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.48,0:03:06.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.86,0:03:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夜襲哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.70,0:03:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夜襲？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.20,0:03:12.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先說清楚  什麼都沒發生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.95,0:03:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真尋  昨晚真是激烈…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.42,0:03:16.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別胡說八道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.71,0:03:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈…奈亞子  然後呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.13,0:03:20.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜此所賜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.72,0:03:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡  孕育著真尋的寶寶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.45,0:03:24.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.62,0:03:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒有  都說了什麼都沒發生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.70,0:03:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且才過了一晚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.25,0:03:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到她說已經有了就應該覺得奇怪了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.04,0:03:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  寶寶動了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.95,0:03:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的！？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.29,0:03:36.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快注意到這是騙人的啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.05,0:03:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微聽聽別人說話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.07,0:03:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,努力了呢  八坂同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.28,0:03:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連余市都這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.95,0:03:44.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饒了我吧  真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.97,0:03:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真  真尋和奈亞子居然…合體了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.92,0:03:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  讓他一直誤會著也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.91,0:03:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是乎  如果是男孩就取名為奈尋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.24,0:04:02.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是女孩就取名為喵亞子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.20,0:04:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真亞子？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.11,0:04:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是真亞子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.96,0:04:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有個小ya的音呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.19,0:04:08.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是喵亞子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.47,0:04:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽也說她兩句啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.12,0:04:14.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙太蹬鼻子上臉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.59,0:04:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要抱第一個孫子了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.62,0:04:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.46,0:04:20.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽  之前你說過的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.78,0:04:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「不可以交往」什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.78,0:04:25.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那話再和這傢伙說一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.60,0:04:27.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個無所謂啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.37,0:04:28.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼！？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.25,0:04:31.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我看出來奈亞子並不是壞孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.38,0:04:36.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就決定  稍稍允許她對小尋展開攻勢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.39,0:04:38.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.00,0:04:40.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但只是「稍稍」哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.67,0:04:43.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟我不會那麼簡單就把小尋交給你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.23,0:04:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢著媽媽  再仔細想想
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.91,0:04:49.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧  真尋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.60,0:04:52.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易得到了母親大人的許可
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.59,0:04:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上舉行婚禮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.97,0:04:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.86,0:05:00.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道真尋想在婚前生第二個孩子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.87,0:05:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,踢死你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.51,0:05:03.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀  不行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.14,0:05:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高中生就要像高中生一樣交往
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.21,0:05:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}你又去拿了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.23,0:05:07.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}嗯  這麵包很好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.61,0:05:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes Mom！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.32,0:05:16.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過父母只要看到孫子的臉就會很快屈服的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.61,0:05:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表情好邪惡  這傢伙一臉壞像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.96,0:05:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總而言之
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.48,0:05:28.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的關係已經得到八坂家的認可了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.11,0:05:29.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝賀你們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.11,0:05:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝賀你們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.83,0:05:30.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.38,0:05:32.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧  真尋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.20,0:05:35.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從kiss開始的戀愛abc
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.41,0:05:40.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先就從誓約的舌吻開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.19,0:05:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是絕對不會認同的！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.75,0:05:56.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被人放置這麼久  還是第一次…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.80,0:06:05.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,0)\pos(250,65)\1c7A2BE3\3c7A2BE3\shad0\fscx75\bord6}青藍SAN瑚礁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.80,0:06:05.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,0)\pos(250,65)\1c7A2BE3\3cFFFFFF\shad0\fscx75}青藍SAN瑚礁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.88,0:06:09.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.03,0:06:13.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真虧她能那樣胡編亂造個沒完
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.67,0:06:17.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  蓮太
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.39,0:06:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼精神啊  不像平時的蓮太
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.99,0:06:28.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  真尋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.75,0:06:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我肯定…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.37,0:06:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能喜愛上真尋和奈亞子的孩子的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.66,0:06:39.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.64,0:06:43.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以讓我們一起認領  撫養他長大…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.09,0:06:45.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦呀  這裡竟然有個Teleporter！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.51,0:06:48.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓮太！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.79,0:06:51.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  真是危險
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.15,0:06:53.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你突然間做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.28,0:06:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他差點跑石頭裡去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.28,0:06:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs20}在石頭中：遊戲Wizardry中  使用Malor定位失敗時出現的提示訊息
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.11,0:06:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要說的就是這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.48,0:06:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kyapi！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.56,0:07:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧  真尋  我們走
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.27,0:07:06.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的真結局路線中  不需要繞遠路的劇情！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.82,0:07:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真尋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.70,0:07:30.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真尋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.84,0:07:33.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真尋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.81,0:07:34.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs20\fad(700,0)}（海濱廁所）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.28,0:07:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  真尋突然不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.45,0:07:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真尋  去哪兒啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.12,0:07:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真尋  別害羞了快出來嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.44,0:07:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  為什麼我會遇到這種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.83,0:08:02.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看那傢伙的狀態  估計就算回到家也沒法一個人清靜下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.35,0:08:03.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}真尋！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.60,0:08:04.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底該如何是好…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.36,0:08:06.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.56,0:08:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  克子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.54,0:08:14.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來海邊也要玩遊戲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.68,0:08:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  讓她來應付奈亞子不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.59,0:08:22.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這新刊超燃的說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.78,0:08:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲  克子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.90,0:08:29.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來  你早飯時在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.34,0:08:31.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在等奈亞子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.12,0:08:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.34,0:08:37.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在不斷地等待中  不知為何滿足了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.98,0:08:43.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說你還真是喜歡老遊戲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.08,0:08:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連到了這裡都在玩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.09,0:08:49.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡…但是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.11,0:08:52.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好空虛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.92,0:08:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克子…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.25,0:08:59.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論玩多少老遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.47,0:09:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都無法填滿因失去Xoth而產生的心中的縫隙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.91,0:09:07.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這麼喜歡Xoth啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.91,0:09:17.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打起精神來  克子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.13,0:09:21.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.34,0:09:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後肯定會有好事降臨的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.67,0:09:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝…謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.71,0:09:29.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.73,0:09:30.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.78,0:09:34.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算立我的Flag也是沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.91,0:09:37.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.29,0:09:40.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在Flag立起來的同時我會全數折斷的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.62,0:09:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦  你們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.33,0:09:46.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼在這裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.39,0:09:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.06,0:09:51.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  去哪了呀真尋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.72,0:09:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬆手  別靠近我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.56,0:09:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈亞子  我昨晚一直等著你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.23,0:09:58.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以請給我獎勵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.31,0:10:01.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可沒東西給你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.02,0:10:05.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊  現在的工作是賣章魚燒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.46,0:10:07.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  在上次事件之後
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.74,0:10:10.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總感覺對各種事物的熱情都被澆滅了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.94,0:10:13.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就像是放下了重擔  好輕鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.46,0:10:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我料理雖然做得不好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.34,0:10:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但唯一被表揚的就是章魚燒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.74,0:10:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  請嘗嘗看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.00,0:10:22.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.98,0:10:24.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開動～了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.53,0:10:26.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.52,0:10:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.08,0:10:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.64,0:10:41.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  不吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.35,0:10:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克蘇魯和蓮太從骨子裡就是天敵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.17,0:10:51.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當初真對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.24,0:10:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我已經不是克蘇魯公司的員工了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.31,0:11:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對你爸爸的公司也不再抱有鬥爭心了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.41,0:11:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我們的關係只是賣章魚燒的和客人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.28,0:11:06.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以放心吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.92,0:11:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.51,0:11:13.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.79,0:11:15.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃  露西小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.88,0:11:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.64,0:11:22.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀  呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.06,0:11:24.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.93,0:11:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.42,0:11:28.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然沒了胃口
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.35,0:11:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得還是別吃這個比較好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.00,0:11:33.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.54,0:11:35.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.08,0:11:37.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都已經吃完了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.31,0:11:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.44,0:11:42.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  應該沒關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.62,0:11:44.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真尋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.52,0:11:47.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我吃掉也可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.53,0:11:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Judgement time！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.58,0:12:00.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真尋  接下來你打算做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.75,0:12:03.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起海濱約會  那可不能錯過那個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.38,0:12:05.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩人在沙灘上奔跑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.20,0:12:09.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在附近的特產店購物也不錯哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.89,0:12:13.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  聽說附近的神社還在辦廟會哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.89,0:12:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們倆去求個順產祝福如何
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.40,0:12:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.32,0:12:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  余市  要去對面岩石堆看看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.96,0:12:23.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃？可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.20,0:12:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  想避人眼目所以去岩石堆二人世界
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.88,0:12:32.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真尋你真是日輪的光輝  也就是「大膽」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.88,0:12:32.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs20}註：大膽和泰坦讀音相似
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.63,0:12:35.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是就近玩個砍西瓜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.87,0:12:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就用我的飛踢和武術來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.87,0:12:42.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是回酒店玩玩牌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.40,0:12:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特別規定每輸一次就脫一件衣服如何
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.72,0:12:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然只要真尋你開口  我隨時…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.94,0:12:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.60,0:12:56.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為啥樣樣都要跟著來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.86,0:13:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這還用說嘛  因為我們倆是比翼鳥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.80,0:13:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺是你砍了我的翅膀  然後硬拼在一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.38,0:13:11.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你瞧那啥  我們倆是連理枝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.48,0:13:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,病枝的話  就得折斷才行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.30,0:13:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真尋  難道說你…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.45,0:13:20.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.13,0:13:24.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是認為不可能有這種事啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.96,0:13:28.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難不成你討厭我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.65,0:13:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  你非得什麼事都挑明了說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.39,0:13:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是嘛  怎麼可能嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.74,0:13:38.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞧我  怎麼問了這麼奇怪的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.05,0:13:40.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我討厭你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.35,0:13:56.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討  討厭…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.95,0:13:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真尋說討厭我…
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------TXTB-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.65,0:14:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有福利喲！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.83,0:14:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  八坂同學  這樣好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.52,0:14:17.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.77,0:14:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.81,0:14:24.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭  討厭…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.65,0:14:27.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牆縫裡有老鼠…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.40,0:14:29.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,窗戶  窗戶上…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.76,0:14:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈亞子的SAN值已經幾乎為零了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.37,0:14:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事  放著不管就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.49,0:14:37.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你確定？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.50,0:14:38.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確定
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.20,0:14:43.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過你看  克子正打算脫奈亞子的泳衣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.86,0:14:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧  奈亞子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.54,0:14:48.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘了那負心漢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.71,0:14:52.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用我特有的技巧使你融化殆盡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.91,0:14:57.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  你打算在大庭廣眾之下做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.30,0:15:00.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從kiss開始的abc？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.80,0:15:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跳躍得太猛了吧  起點完全不對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.69,0:15:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.82,0:15:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們都是外星人  所以不會觸犯條例的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.82,0:15:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs20}註：暗指《東京都青少年健全育成條例修正案》
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.39,0:15:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這是在向誰挑釁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.93,0:15:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然  這時是不是該小尋出場了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.05,0:15:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.44,0:15:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是有點懊悔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.50,0:15:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.33,0:15:30.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小尋和媽媽都被奈亞子救過
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.67,0:15:32.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.87,0:15:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.32,0:15:39.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭  討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.53,0:15:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈亞子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.10,0:15:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  奈亞子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.93,0:15:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真尋說他討厭我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.14,0:15:46.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用英語說就是「mine」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.01,0:15:48.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是水雷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.01,0:15:48.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs20}註:日語中的水雷與討厭同音
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.53,0:15:51.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽我說  奈亞子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.51,0:15:53.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.85,0:15:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才說討厭你其實是騙你的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.83,0:16:01.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…我喜歡你勝過刺身配菜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.86,0:16:03.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刺身配菜？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.35,0:16:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該也勝過雞蛋裡那白色的黏狀物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.18,0:16:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那黏狀物很噁心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.87,0:16:17.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們去海濱小屋休息下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.06,0:16:18.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.07,0:16:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  你剛才說的特產店啊還有廟會什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.91,0:16:28.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要去逛逛？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.18,0:16:31.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈亞子？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.80,0:16:39.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.92,0:16:42.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想和奈亞子約會
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.46,0:16:44.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想和真尋約會
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.87,0:16:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以打擾他們哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.41,0:16:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.48,0:16:56.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真尋  快點啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.16,0:17:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們先去哪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.08,0:17:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別黏著我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.37,0:17:10.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨便  你想去哪就去哪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.44,0:17:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.30,0:17:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是  這是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.06,0:17:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是約會必備的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.02,0:17:40.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起喝嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.81,0:17:42.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不要  羞死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.47,0:17:45.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好好  你贏了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.28,0:17:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦  真尋也快喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.70,0:17:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  好了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.69,0:17:56.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不去！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.85,0:17:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs20\fad(300,0)}（秘寶館=性博物館）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.60,0:17:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這麼說嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.47,0:17:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不要啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.77,0:18:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.24,0:18:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對不要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.18,0:18:07.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你變白也沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.35,0:18:08.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.70,0:18:10.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們去那兒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.97,0:18:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說那神社求姻緣很靈哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.43,0:18:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好又在辦廟會
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.25,0:18:20.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.97,0:18:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說  邪神可以來參拜神社的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.53,0:18:40.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.17,0:18:48.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不由地想起以前去過的廟會
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.56,0:18:50.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙也有廟會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.78,0:18:53.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有哦  一年兩次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.08,0:18:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盂蘭盆會時和年末時在宇宙有明國際展覽中心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.93,0:18:58.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那絕對不是廟會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.22,0:18:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}排隊請接著這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.74,0:19:00.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很熱鬧哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.26,0:19:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又幹嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.03,0:19:06.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞好嘞  謝謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.74,0:19:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,線香煙火喲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.69,0:19:12.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們倆一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.27,0:19:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.15,0:19:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不起眼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.61,0:19:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為太陽太耀眼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.88,0:19:30.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那擋住夕陽的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.16,0:19:35.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺要比剛才漂亮點了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.43,0:19:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滅了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.31,0:19:43.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  還真美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.16,0:19:47.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然天還沒黑  不怎麼起眼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.74,0:19:49.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此  也還是很美
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.56,0:19:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  奈亞子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.00,0:19:55.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.95,0:19:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在神社祈求時很虔誠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.48,0:20:02.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你許了什麼願？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.99,0:20:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.46,0:20:08.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.83,0:20:11.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.12,0:20:15.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望能永遠和真尋在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.83,0:20:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我許的這個願
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.93,0:20:21.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說些啥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.26,0:20:28.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈亞子  我們回去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.02,0:20:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多該吃晚飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.78,0:20:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽她們也在等我們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.92,0:20:39.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.63,0:20:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.73,0:20:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們繞繞路再回去好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.46,0:20:48.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.19,0:20:52.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼不可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.78,0:20:57.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧  真尋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.13,0:21:07.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.37,0:21:08.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.08,0:21:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的夢想就是有一天能和所愛之人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.61,0:21:15.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起漫步在佈滿晚霞的沙灘上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.27,0:21:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢想成真了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.76,0:21:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你瞎說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.80,0:21:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說了什麼奇怪的話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.20,0:21:26.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.83,0:21:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平時的話  明明會對我死纏爛打
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.23,0:21:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然變得那麼乖巧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.00,0:21:35.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  我根本不相信你喜歡我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.04,0:21:37.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你整天開玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.87,0:21:39.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老說些隨便的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.94,0:21:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.23,0:21:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是不裝作開玩笑  「喜歡你」會很難說出口的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.95,0:21:54.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而  這確實是我不帶任何虛假的真心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.64,0:21:55.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我說幾遍都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.11,0:22:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜歡真尋了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------NEXT-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.84,0:23:43.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次由我們來負責預告喲  夏塔君
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.83,0:23:45.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點緊張了啊
