Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.95,0:23:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(160,160)\fs16\1c000000\bord0\shad0}奈亞子  進擊love heart
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.95,0:23:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(460,165)\fs16\1c000000\bord0\shad0}蓮太  一萬兩千年前就想與你合體
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.95,0:23:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(160,260)\fs16\1c000000\bord0\shad0}克子  勇往墮落  desire
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.95,0:23:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(460,265)\fs16\1c000000\bord0\shad0}珠緒  認真戀愛前555秒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.70,0:23:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一話「奈亞子的『心跳高中』」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.32,0:23:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不由想起  我學生時代的心境
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.73,0:23:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能對奇怪的事直言不諱說奇怪的勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.94,0:23:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為媽媽的裙子太短了很奇怪


